Thank you @thefliphubb, @the_denise_project, @wild.hearts.home, @crystelmontenegrohome, @eternalharvestdecor, @dibsdeco, and @jewelconfections for all the time and love you gave to Tia’s home. 💛💛 So beyond grateful for you guys making this happen!

Here is my news!!! So excited!!! I feels so strongly about finding peace with where you are in life and I think it is so important to find that peace within your home! I know some are just struggling to get by day by day and don’t have the time, energy, or finances to create that peaceful space in their home. This is where I want to help!! The plan: Find deserving people and give them one space in their home where they can find that peace that they so desperately need! 
How you guys can help? Share this! I need your help to find those that deserve a makeover. DM me your nominations! If you don’t have know anyone that needs help I would love if you could share this! Thank you in advance!! 🤍🤍🤍 #buildinghope #buildingpeace #buildsbykristen #diy #charitybuilds #diy #doityourself #peace #hope

Bus Reveal!! (Part 1) I cannot believe I’m here... done with the bus! #ad I poured my heart and soul into this bus for the past six months and it was SO worth it! Would I do it again?? Don’t ask me right now. Haha!

We wanted peace of mind while we were out adventuring! Our new @bluebyadt camera does just that! It was so easy to set up and we can check in on the bus from the app on our phones! So easy!

This was one of my favorite transformations I’ve done so far! When I asked @thetiabeestokes what room she wanted to have made over she said this room. She is always thinking of her kids and others. 💛 Swipe to see the before!

I got this rug and all the other rugs in this transformation from @boutiquerugs! I’m obsessed with the rug in this room! Definitely getting this one for my home! 

The AMAZING wallpaper is by @indigodesign.co! 😍 

The bedding is from @beddys! If you haven’t checked out Beddy’s yet I would!! The kids will now be able to make their own bed with how easy these are to make! 

The cute chair is from @shabundysprovo! It’s perfect and was an amazing price!
